trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of application related commands.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um conjunto padrão de comandos relacionados ao aplicativo.

trans-unit.source: The commands in the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> class and commands in the other command library classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> and <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, are intended to represent a set of common commands that application programmers encounter frequently.
trans-unit.target: Os comandos de <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands> classe e comandos no outro comando classes de biblioteca, tais como <xref:System.Windows.Input.ComponentCommands> e <xref:System.Windows.Input.NavigationCommands>, serve para representar um conjunto de comandos comuns que os programadores de aplicativos com frequência encontram.

trans-unit.source: The commands only represent the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> and not the implementation logic for the command.
trans-unit.target: Os comandos representam apenas a instância das <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> e não a lógica de implementação do comando.

trans-unit.source: The implementation logic is bound to the command with a <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>.
trans-unit.target: A lógica de implementação está associada ao comando com um <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding>.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Close%2A> command is executed on a control, the logic which performs the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Close%2A> command may not be provided by the control, so the application writer will be responsible for writing the logic that determines how the control will handle the command.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, se o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Close%2A> comando é executado em um controle, a lógica que executa o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Close%2A> comando não pode ser fornecida pelo controle, então o gravador de aplicativos será responsável por gravar a lógica que determina como o controle tratará o comando.

trans-unit.source: Many controls do provide implementation logic for many of the commands in the command library.
trans-unit.target: Muitos controles fornecer lógica de implementação para muitos dos comandos na biblioteca de comandos.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> class provides logic for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> commands.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox> classe fornece lógica para o <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Paste%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Cut%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Copy%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Undo%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.Input.ApplicationCommands.Redo%2A> comandos.

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding see the [Commanding Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre comandos e comando, consulte o [visão geral do comando](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/commanding-overview.md).

trans-unit.source: Gets the value that represents the Cancel Print command.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor que representa o comando Cancelar Impressão.

trans-unit.source: This command indicates intention to cancel a print job.
trans-unit.target: Este comando indica a intenção de cancelar um trabalho de impressão.

trans-unit.source: There is not necessarily an implementation for the command on any given object; in many cases the implementation for the command is the responsibility of the application writer.
trans-unit.target: Não há necessariamente uma implementação para o comando de qualquer objeto especificado; em muitos casos, a implementação do comando é responsabilidade do gravador de aplicativos.

trans-unit.source: Represents a command which is always ignored.
trans-unit.target: Representa um comando que é sempre ignorado.

trans-unit.source: This command is always ignored and does not handle the input event that caused it.

trans-unit.source: This provides a way to turn off an input binding built into an existing control.
